      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver that won't break the bank? This vehicle is ready to get you where you need to go! It\u2019s a solid, functional choice that has been well-maintained mechanically, though it does show some honest cosmetic wear and tear from regular use. Perfect for someone who prioritizes dependability and value over a showroom finish!",
