      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. It runs smoothly and is mechanically sound, making it a reliable choice for daily commuting or long trips. While the exterior and interior show some minor signs of normal wear and tear, such as small surface scratches and light upholstery aging, there are no major mechanical issues or structural damage. You can expect a dependable driving experience with a clean title and a history of regular servicing.",
